          "settings": {
            "about_heading": "Free shipping & returns",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "about_heading_content": "<p>Enjoy hassle-free shopping with our unbeatable offer of free shipping and returns. Browse our stylish collection from the comfort of your home, and have your favorite items delivered to your doorstep without any additional cost. If something doesn't fit or meet your expectations, don't worry! We've got you covered with our free and easy returns. Shop with confidence and experience the ultimate convenience with our free shipping and returns policy.</p>"
